TC-001. Verify Home Page Loads Successfully

Preconditions: User has internet access.

Steps:

Open the website.
Wait until the page is fully loaded.

Expected Result:
The page loads without errors.
Logo, title, illustrations, and CTA button are displayed.
No broken images or layout issues are present.

TC-002. Verify Responsive Layout

Steps:

Open the page on Desktop.
Open the page on Tablet.
Open the page on Mobile.

Expected Result:
All elements are displayed correctly.
No overlapping content.
The page is usable on all supported screen sizes.
Play For Free Button

TC-003. Verify "PLAY FOR FREE" Button Visibility

Steps:

Open the landing page.

Expected Result:
The "PLAY FOR FREE" button is visible.
Button text is readable and properly aligned.
TC-004. Verify Navigation via "PLAY FOR FREE" Button

Steps:

Click the "PLAY FOR FREE" button.

Expected Result:
User is redirected to the game page or game launch screen.
No 404, 500, or other system errors occur.

TC-005. Verify Button Clickable Area

Steps:

Click the center of the button.
Click each edge of the button.

Expected Result:
The button responds to clicks across its entire visible area.
Cookie Consent Banner

TC-006. Verify Cookie Banner Appears for New User

Preconditions: Clear browser cookies.

Steps:

Open the website.

Expected Result:
Cookie consent banner is displayed.

TC-007. Verify "Accept All" Functionality

Steps:

Click the "Accept All" button.

Expected Result:
Cookie banner closes.
Consent is saved.
Banner does not reappear after page refresh.

TC-008. Verify "Customise" Functionality

Steps:

Click the "Customise" button.

Expected Result:
Cookie preference settings are displayed.
User can manage cookie categories.
TC-009. Verify Cookie Preferences Persistence

Steps:

Open cookie settings.
Change preferences.
Save changes.
Refresh the page.

Expected Result:

Selected preferences remain saved.
Banner does not reappear unnecessarily.
Language Selector

TC-010. Verify Language Selector Visibility

Steps:

Open the landing page.

Expected Result:
Language selector is displayed in the top-right corner.

TC-011. Verify Language Change

Steps:

Open the language dropdown.
Select another available language.

Expected Result:
All page content is translated into the selected language.
No untranslated strings are visible.
TC-012. Verify Language Persistence

Steps:

Change the language.
Refresh the page.

Expected Result:

The selected language remains active.
