Negative Testing

TC-015. Verify Behavior with JavaScript Disabled

Steps:

Disable JavaScript in the browser.
Open the website.

Expected Result:

Page degrades gracefully or displays a meaningful message.
No critical rendering failures occur.
TC-016. Verify Behavior on Slow Network

Steps:

Enable Slow 3G network throttling in DevTools.
Reload the page.

Expected Result:
Page loads successfully.
Loading indicators or placeholders are displayed if applicable.
No broken UI elements appear.
